{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"514c06e4ab","title":"叶剑英传达毛主席的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"de381f801f","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":27,"articleId":"514c06e4ab"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"bcecfeaa3a","name":"叶剑英","type":"人物"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"},{"id":"eee1eed029","name":"叶剑英"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9d9a390330","type":"title","text":"叶剑英传达毛主席的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"514c06e4ab"},{"id":"e68e24737b","type":"paragraph","text":"一、我认为十三个军区不要同时搞，要有前有后。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"514c06e4ab"},{"id":"edbb48615c","type":"paragraph","text":"二、地方文化大革命正在猛烈开展，夺权斗争还在激烈进行，我们军队要支持革命左派进行斗争，因此军队和地方文化大革命要差开。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"514c06e4ab"},{"id":"4bf49ae7ab","type":"paragraph","text":"三、现在国际上帝、修、反正利用我们文化大革命继续大搞反华活动。如苏联在镇压学生，新疆边境飞机活动增多了。地面部队要有所警惕，要有所准备。如济南、南京、福州、广州、昆明等地区。所以文化大革命时间要稍推一下。将来一定要搞的，顾大局。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"514c06e4ab"}],"page":{"id":"b73c55a1ef","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"514c06e4ab","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}